Everest Buys Premiere to Expand in Canada Sports, Entertainment

-- B y   A p r i l   L e e
-- 
2011-02-11T19:20:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-11/everest-buys-premiere-to-expand-in-canada-sports-entertainment.html
Everest Re. Group Ltd., the Bermuda-
based insurer and reinsurer, acquired Premiere Underwriting
Services to add business in entertainment, sports and leisure in  Canada .  Toronto-based Premiere will be an affiliate of Everest
Insurance Company of Canada, Everest said today in a statement
distributed by Business Wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
April Lee in New York at 
 Alee355@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
